<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`RecursiveGraphNeuralNetwork`<sp/>class,<sp/>implemented<sp/>in<sp/>Cython,<sp/>represents<sp/>a<sp/>specific<sp/>implementation<sp/>of<sp/>a<sp/>Recursive<sp/>Graph<sp/>Neural<sp/>Network<sp/>(RGNN)<sp/>model<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework.<sp/>It<sp/>inherits<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>generic<sp/>`ModelTemplate`<sp/>class,<sp/>extending<sp/>its<sp/>functionalities<sp/>to<sp/>incorporate<sp/>features<sp/>and<sp/>structures<sp/>relevant<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>RGNN<sp/>architecture.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>high-performance<sp/>interface<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>RGNN<sp/>model,<sp/>enabling<sp/>efficient<sp/>training<sp/>and<sp/>inference<sp/>for<sp/>hierarchical<sp/>graph-based<sp/>data.</highlight></codeline>
